    | tcp://127.0.0.1:28015        |      | storage + triproxies          |
    \------------------------------/      | Android provider              |
                                          | iOS provider (host-bridge)    |
                                          | Samsung worker (optional)     |
                                          \---------------+---------------/
                                                          |
                        ZMQ dev bus                       |
                 (connect-sub/connect-push)              |
                                                          v
                                     /-----------------------------------\
