                                     | SUB: tcp://127.0.0.1:9394         |
                                     | topic: devEvent                   |
                                     | intro/present/heartbeat           |
                                     | install/uninstall/launch          |
                                     | ios-deploy + devicectl fallback   |
                                     | tap/home/type/screenshot via WDA  |
